---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Work With Me — Michał Parkoła"
  description="I help software founders scale delivery and operations from 5 to 50 people."
>
  <div class="page">
    <h1>Work with me</h1>

    <p class="lede">
      I help software founders who've outgrown the "everyone does everything" phase
      but aren't yet big enough for a full C-suite. I bring structure to delivery,
      operations and people — so you can focus on product and customers.
    </p>

    <section>
      <h2>How I can help</h2>

      <div class="modes">
        <div class="mode">
          <h3>Head of Delivery</h3>
          <p>
            Full-time, embedded in your team. I own the delivery process end-to-end:
            sprint cadence, cross-team coordination, shipping predictability, removing
            bottlenecks. You stop being the project manager.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mode">
          <h3>Fractional COO</h3>
          <p>
            Part-time, typically 2-3 days/week. I set up and run the operational
            backbone — hiring pipelines, team structure, planning rhythms, internal
            communication — so the company works even when you're not in every meeting.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mode">
          <h3>Management Consulting</h3>
          <p>
            Focused engagements for specific problems: scaling the team, fixing a broken
            delivery process, preparing for a growth phase. I diagnose, recommend and
            help implement — then get out of the way.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Who this is for</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Software founders running companies with <strong>5-50 people</strong></li>
        <li>You've proven product-market fit but delivery is becoming the bottleneck</li>
        <li>You're hiring faster than you can onboard</li>
        <li>You know you need management structure but don't want bureaucracy</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Background</h2>
      <p>
        15+ years in software — from hands-on engineering through senior engineering
        management and agile coaching. I've scaled teams, shipped products and built
        the processes that let both happen repeatably. I write about delivery, teams
        and leadership on <a href="/">this blog</a> and have published
        <a href="https://michalparkola.gumroad.com/">several books</a> on the topic.
      </p>
      <p>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/michalparkola/">Full background on LinkedIn →</a>
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="cta">
      <h2>Let's talk</h2>
      <p>
        Email me at <a href="mailto:michal@michalparkola.com">michal@michalparkola.com</a>
        with a few sentences about your situation. I'll reply within 2 business days.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page {
    max-width: 100%;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: #2c3e50;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .lede {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #444;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: #2c3e50;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .modes {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .mode {
    border: 1px solid #eee;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .mode h3 {
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: #2c3e50;
  }

  .mode p {
    margin: 0;
    color: #555;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  ul {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #444;
  }

  li {
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  p {
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #444;
  }

  a {
    color: #5C8D11;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .cta {
    background: #f8f9fa;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .cta p {
    margin-bottom: 0;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .lede {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
    }
  }
</style>
